original_conversation
So my friend was driving in Poland and got a ticket from policeman. He was on the same road today and noticed this magic thing.
What is it
Lights off= 80 Lights on= 30 actual speed limit.
It's just the opposite. The color reflects black at day. The poin is to make people drive slower during the day.
